{"tid":1154753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[上山下鄉 返鄉創業又贏]中國打擊美農出絕招： 補貼政策+增地種植大豆","createTime":"2019-05-14T13:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T00:06:30.000Z","uid":54733,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f312dbccc4d3148f69f95b92b81e203e34774e63","tid":1154753,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190514/large/1557825193_d7f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557825193_d7f7.jpg&h=6c559b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美貿易戰升級，中國已部署打擊美國的豆農。據央視網報道，中國去年大幅減少進口美國大豆，令美國大豆產區的農民受到重創。中國東北地區現正「春播」（春天播種），今年大豆種植面積大幅增加，料中國對美國的大豆採購量還會繼續下滑。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，中國政府為了鼓勵大豆種植，今年推出補貼政策。每畝大豆補貼340元人民幣（約387港元），比種植粟米的補貼每畝高出295元（約336港元）。政策引導提高了農民種豆的積極性。<br />\n<br />\n有中國「大豆之鄉」之稱的黑龍江省海倫市，種植大戶都不約而同擴種大豆。海倫市副市長王寶峰表示，今年大豆種植面積達到260萬畝，比去年提高了60萬畝。面積增加的主要原因有兩個：一是政府推出了大豆振興計劃，農民看到了政策紅利；二是市場價格不錯，農民覺得效益好。<br />\n<br />\n今年初，中國農業農村部發佈《大豆振興計劃實施方案》，將擴大中國東北、黃淮海和西南地區的大豆種植面積。2019年大豆面積增加1,000萬畝。根據中國農業農村部的最新數據顯示，截至5月10日，全國已播種各類農作物8.4億畝，完成意向面積6成以上。其中，大豆已播種37.4%，黑龍江和內蒙古種植面積增幅顯著。<br />\n央視網/ 多維新聞網"},{"pid":"d4bf59422c18559a81b73f0584e8656d811fa6ab","tid":1154753,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"返鄉創業又嬴"},{"pid":"76ba871f3e21ddd21ed06b19d878bba3f344b772","tid":1154753,"uid":44454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"正，好快有豆香味嘅秋行軍蟲食"},{"pid":"583ac5193411350f7091734d338fc92dc5f6d5a8","tid":1154753,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"下年d多到唔撚值錢，支那歷史上出現過幾多次"},{"pid":"4d3511dde9794bc0d1f1a7e0272960383dec63bd","tid":1154753,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"583ac5193411350f7091734d338fc92dc5f6d5a8","tid":1154753,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"下年d多到唔撚值錢，支那歷史上出現過幾多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"又黎大躍進"},{"pid":"510d0da76bfe7fc500addec42155d707d1e74b95","tid":1154753,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ba871f3e21ddd21ed06b19d878bba3f344b772","tid":1154753,"uid":44454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"正，好快有豆香味嘅秋行軍蟲食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"含豐富蛋白質"},{"pid":"1609fa8d785daa465b0e88cf89e9e3c625657e24","tid":1154753,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"D地起哂樓同工廠好難變返農地種野架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d737c91140b086a99baa8ccc739345e82b269f","tid":1154753,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ba871f3e21ddd21ed06b19d878bba3f344b772","tid":1154753,"uid":44454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"正，好快有豆香味嘅秋行軍蟲食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"蛋白質翻倍，賺翻了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9916fd0f3a5203e0209a93a7e9e00d6bb3720530","tid":1154753,"uid":162535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1609fa8d785daa465b0e88cf89e9e3c625657e24","tid":1154753,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"D地起哂樓同工廠好難變返農地種野架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"種到，但有毒"},{"pid":"9f79a372f3563902f3d476400c50799132a35767","tid":1154753,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"農村發大財!!!!"},{"pid":"9d11ab44edf935a9e176b80f057898f1de67dee2","tid":1154753,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1609fa8d785daa465b0e88cf89e9e3c625657e24","tid":1154753,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"D地起哂樓同工廠好難變返農地種野架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"含重金屬者"},{"pid":"e7108b695c80324a7354a346af3bc0f2dad1aa9b","tid":1154753,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰爆發】中國打擊美農出絕招： 補貼政策+增地種植大豆<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190514/59599967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599967&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=a61c8eee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599967&h=ba8c4cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190514/59599967</a>"},{"pid":"ebff0521ade77ed01747016c11d622dc6a3e2356","tid":1154753,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"諗起大躍進d口號"},{"pid":"8ba0b9bf17421a224ee35dce944e2afac49a650f","tid":1154753,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"大躍進2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當老共一意孤行 表示真係堅決要鎖國打仗 個市凍過水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66991e02245e03992235203edaa5bba2f2232686","tid":1154753,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d11ab44edf935a9e176b80f057898f1de67dee2","tid":1154753,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1609fa8d785daa465b0e88cf89e9e3c625657e24","tid":1154753,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"D地起哂樓同工廠好難變返農地種野架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"含重金屬者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"中國人食開元素週期表所有元素，唔怕啦，又贏。"},{"pid":"6422aad0ab06f9bd1819076be07e13dfc5fa7c60","tid":1154753,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"2、自己種大豆「不划算」<br />\n<br />\n為什麼不自己種大豆，非要進口美國大豆，主要是大豆是一種「土地密集型」經濟作物，單位，我國人多地少，種植大豆沒有天然優勢，而且大豆的單位面積產量只有水稻、小麥、玉米的1/3~1/4，種植起來不划算。<br />\n<br />\n用數據簡單說明：2016年，我國大豆播種面積達到710萬公頃，相當於1.07億畝，總產量達到1310萬噸。同年，進口大豆8391萬噸，如果把進口大豆都換成國產大豆，那麼需要把大豆的播種面積提高到7.9億畝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3、種單產高的糧食作物更合適<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n如果把全國1/3的耕地播種面積拿來種大豆，大豆是可以做到自給自足，但是糧食、蔬菜、水果就需要進口了。</strong></span></span>另外，我國2016年水稻和小麥的總播種面積是8.1億畝，與生產9700萬噸大豆所需要的7.9億畝耕地相當，但是小麥和水稻產量的總產量是3.4億噸，是同面積大豆產量的3.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sohu.com/a/243518214_490881/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F243518214_490881%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c40ec81c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sohu.com/a/243518214_490881/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a>"},{"pid":"f4b5415f354f13ba1b2c36451d249e153b2c5511","tid":1154753,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"人有多大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958ab4c42fcb3674165e1961cde25916fd82a6c3","tid":1154753,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4b5415f354f13ba1b2c36451d249e153b2c5511","tid":1154753,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"人有多大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"豆有多大產 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3aaeb5667fce9446f274a26c3f5284c4b71a0b","tid":1154753,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:03:57.000Z","msg":"唔種米？"},{"pid":"f04447fae5b990ed164dd6680303caa393d91f62","tid":1154753,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"大陸爆發秋行軍蟲災，種幾多都無用"}]}